This directory includes the SQLite source code in the form of the
official "amalgamation".

The files "sqlite3.c" and "sqlite3.h" were obtained from the SQLite
project:
 Source: https://github.com/sqlite/sqlite/releases/tag/version-3.33.0
 Amalgamation created with: ./configure && make sqlite3.c

Note: The GitHub repository is a mirror of the official SQLite source,
which is maintained via Fossil at https://sqlite.org.
